years_succeeded.description:
Years with at least one succeeded `backfill_run` (kind `backfill`);
pre-0011 history is log-only, so early years may show data without a
run row.

epoch.description:
Rollout epoch (`agents/EPOCHS.md`): 1 = launch set, 2 = Brazil, …;
`null` for the un-scheduled long tail the factory orders by
`priority_score`.

YearProgress.description:
One filing-year bucket. `year` is `extract(year from filing.filed_date)`;
a filing without a `filed_date` lands in the honest `year: null` bucket —
`external_id` is NEVER parsed for a year (its shape is regime-specific).

